        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The scheme “Scholarships to Meritorious Students of Sanskrit Schools” is implemented by the Directorate of Sanskrit Education under the Department of Sanskrit Education, Government of Uttarakhand. The scheme aims to promote Sanskrit education by providing scholarships to meritorious students of Prathmik Madhyama (Class 10) and Uttar Madhyama (Class 12) in Sanskrit schools who secure the highest marks.\n<br>\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n1. Meritorious students of Prathmik Madhyama (Class 10) are awarded a scholarship of ₹500 per month for 20 months.\n1. Three meritorious students of Uttar Madhyama (Class 12) are awarded cash prizes:\n\n\n- **First Position:** ₹20,000/-- **Second Position:** ₹15,000/-- **Third Position:** ₹10,000/-\n<br>\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The scheme aims to promote Sanskrit education by providing scholarships to meritorious students of Prathmik Madhyama (Class 10) and Uttar Madhyama (Class 12) in Sanskrit schools who secure the highest marks.",
