          "process_md": "\n  - The student’s application is first forwarded and recommended by the school principal, and then by the Assistant Director of the respective district.\n  - Required documents include the Aadhaar card, bank account details, and the merit list certificate.\n  - If the student’s name appears in the merit list, they or their guardian can submit the application online through the [Apuni Sarkar portal](https://eservices.uk.gov.in/) during the same session.\n<br>\n\n"
