      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n   1. The applicant must be a student of a recognized Sanskrit school under the Uttarakhand Sanskrit Shiksha Parishad.\n   1. The applicant must have secured a place in the top 10 in the class 10th merit list or in the top 3 in the class 12th merit list from the Board Examination of Sanskrit School.   1. The applicant must be currently studying in class 11th or 12th after clearing class 10th.\n&lt;br&gt;\n\n<br>\n\n",
